1. How to enter the DATABASE:
- open cmd
- cd C:\work\musicrypt
- sqlite\sqlite3.exe musicrypt\db.sqlite3

DATABASE COMMANDS:
- . tables
- SELECT * FROM base_encryptedfile;
- DELETE FROM base_encryptedfile WHERE id=1;


2. How to run the APPLICATION:
- open cmd
- cd C:\work\musicrypt --> goes into the top project directory
- env\Scripts\activate  --> activates the virtual environment
- cd musicrypt
- python manage.py runserver
- open Chrome and go to localhost:8000


3. Project STRUCTURE:
- base/models --> describes what goes into the database
- base/urls --> describes URLs
- base/crypto --> provides functions for encryption and decryption of files
- base/views --> describes pages and logic
- base/templates --> HTML files (what the browser reads and displays)
- base/static --> CSS (styles) and Bootstrap


4. Project ADMINISTRATION:
- Go to localhost:8000/admin
